@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.sin(v1 + 0.80) * 0.58))
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 * v2))
    v0 = 0.89
    v0 = 0.86
    tmp = (v1 * wp.exp((tmp + 0.20 - v0 + 0.46)))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = ((0.88 - 0.98) - (v0 + v2))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.39) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.85)) + wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.94)))
    data[tid] = v0
